Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:49.22,Default - A,,0,0,0,,만세~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.36,Default - A,,0,0,0,,만세, 만세~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:51.41,Default - A,,0,0,0,,만세, 만세, 만세~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:52.40,Default - A,,0,0,0,,만세, 만세, 만세, 만세~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,훌륭하게!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,합격을 쟁취해내고\N행복 가득~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,..일 줄 알았던\N고토 히토리를
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,막아서는\N거대한 벽!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,그것은―!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 목표 할당량\N5장~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드 멤버랑 가족 말고는\N아는 사람이 없는데, 대 핀치!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,어쩌지?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,어쩔 거야!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,고토~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:07.58,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\fna두리둥실\frz17.21\t(00,300,\fscx60)\t(300,560,\fscx40)\move(1130,565,1200,520,00,560)}허어~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:08.48,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\fna두리둥실\frz17.21\fscx40)\pos(1145,540)\t(00,100,\fscx200\fscy150\frz10)\t(100,200,\fscx80\fscy80\frz3)\t(200,300,\fscx100\fscy100\frz0)}허어~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브까지는\N앞으로 10일밖에 남았는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.18,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs70\bord0\pos(960,830)}어젯밤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,헤헤...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,아부지
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,어무이
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,동생
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,개...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,나머지 한 장은...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,할머..니?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,하..하지만\N라이브 때문에
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,힘들게 편도 3시간이나\N되는 길을...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:31.17,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(1495,450)}먹어도 돼!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,아무리 그래도\N지미헨은 못 가지 않겠니?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 여..역시!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,응~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,아니...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,그건 아무래도\N나도 그러지 않을까아
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,..하고
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,생각{\fs73}은 {\fs71}했{\fs69}는{\fs67}데 {\fs62}말{\fs55}야{\fs50}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고~
