Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이렇게\N허세 부릴까!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아니, 솔직하게...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}"할당량 못 채워~"\N이럴까...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하지만 그러면...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,목표 할당량도 못 파는\N사람은 모가지야♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,바이바이, 봇치
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,선배~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,제 넓고 깊은 인맥을\N이용해서~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,멋지고 성격 밝은\N기타리스트를 찾아왔어요~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,이-예이~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ㄹㄹㄹㄹㄹ롹큐~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실}-웨이~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,700)\fna두리둥실}-록뀨~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,하흑...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,으아아...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 난 엄마한테\N그런 똥폼을 잡은 거야~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,허...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,사, 사...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,사람이 쓰러졌...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,어..어쩌지!?\N마..말 걸어야...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,아..아니, 그보다도!!\N구..구급차!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 여보세요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}삐~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}오후 4시 30분이 됐음을\N알려드립―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,물...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,물 쥬세여...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,바..바로 저 앞에서\N사올게요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,그거 말고도\N숙취해소약...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,윽...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,또 바지락 된장국...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,죽도 먹고 싶어...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,간호받을 곳은...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}쨍쨍한 날에 막 말린\N푹신푹신 침대 위에서어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}지..진짜 이때다 하고\N주문 폭발하는데...
