Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,어...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,저기,\N그럼 저는 이만...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 이름 뭐라고 해~?
