Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩도 마실래~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,싼 술이긴 한데!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,응?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩은\N미성년자였던가~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,근데 어라?\N듣고 있니~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:48.38,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿왜 아까부터\N아무 말도 안 해주는 거야~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:48.94,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿아!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.21,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿히토리쨩\N몸 차갑다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.99,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿뭔 콘크리트 같은데!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:53.67,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿헤에, 헤...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.65,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿어..어, 어쩔래?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.21,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿수..술 마실까, 역시!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.11,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿{\fad(00,600)}으헤헤헿...
