Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저는 이만...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿{\fad(00,1500)}어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,오오, 기타~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,칠 줄 알아?\N기타~?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,나도 밴드 하거든~\N인디지만 말야~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.84,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿있지,\N진짜 칠 줄 알아?
