Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,어흐흑...\N그랬구나...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩은\N비극의 소녀였단 건가~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어..엄청\N동정해주고 있어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 파는 거\N엄청 힘들지~?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,나도 초창기 때는\N엄청 괴로웠는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그러셨군요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,좋아~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,생명의 은인을 위해\N내가 한꺼풀 벗어줘야지!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,어...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 준비해!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}나랑 네가 같이...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,지금부터 여기서\N버스킹을 조지는 거야♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실\fs90\bord6}느ㅖ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,버..버스킹이요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,맞아~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,전단지도 있는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,버스킹으로\N이목을 끌어서~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 사달라고 하는 게\N제일 직빵이라니깐~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.30,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord6\frx6\fry12\frz356.6\pos(240,355)\c&H8B478F&\3c&HB4E5F9&}교통규제 {\fs45}알림
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.30,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord2\c&H3F58D1&\3c&H304497&\frx12\fry14\frz357.6\pos(570,470)}오늘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.30,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna천생연분\fs40\bord5\c&H3A4FB8&\3c&HABD2EF&\frx2\fry8\frz1.866\pos(260,855)}이 도로는 차량통행이 불가하게 됩니다{\fs25}\N\N{\fs40}협력 부탁드립니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 이 부근에서\N축제하는 모양인지
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,사람도 많고
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,버스킹 하기\N딱 좋은 날이라니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,아
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도 앰프나\N버스킹용 기재가 아무것도 없나...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그럼~\N아쉽지만 다음 기회에...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 여보세요?\N저예여~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,사라이써용~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,지금부터\N길거리 공연할 건데
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,기재 갖고 와줌 안 됨?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.57,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿아, 기재만 있으면\N되니깐~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.65,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿응, 맞아
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.15,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿고맙고용~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어..어쩌지...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}점점 얘기가\N진행되는데!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.03,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fn태 나무\fs70\bord6\c&H101010&\3c&H9A91A3&\frx6\fry0\frz353.7\pos(1250,105)}결속밴드
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,여러분~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,지금부터\N라이브합니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,공짜니까 한가하면\N보고 가쥬세여~
