Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,카나자와핫케이\N주민 여러분~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,지금부터\N라이브합니당~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,보고 가주세영~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,와아아~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,기대된다아~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,아니,\N너도 해야지?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐~?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,밖에서는\N기타 쳐본 적이 없어?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게나 무서우면\N눈 감고 치는 건 어때?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,..는 넝담이고~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그거라면 괜찮을지도...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.31,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿쑥스럼쟁이구나~\N그럴 수 있지~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}항상 손도 잘 안 보이는\N어둠 속에서 계속 쳤었으니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}응...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}괜찮을 거 같아...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만\N일단 말해두겠는데
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.58,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,10)\fs200\bord0\blur3\fscx500\fscy300\alpha&H60&\c&H394B59&\3c&H958999&\pos(1460,350)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.58,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\fad(500,10)\fn태 나무\fs70\bord6\c&H171C18&\3c&H958999&\pos(1460,400)}스페셜 라이브\N{\fs60}티켓 사줘!\N\N―――결속밴드―――\N\N{\fs50}1장 1500엔입니~다\N\N8/14 18시 시모키타자와 스태리
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,지금 눈 앞에 있는 사람들은\N네가 싸울 상대가 아니거든?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,적이 누군지\N착각하면 안 된다~?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}적...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.42,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs60\move(630,725,645,735,00,300)}븨헤~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}적이라는 건\N또 무슨 소리...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,네?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,학교에서의\N고토 씨요?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,맞아...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,상상이 되냐면\N되기는 하는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,그게...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,역시 아싸찐따야?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord3\pos(985,912)}봇치
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,에둘러 표현할 줄을\N모르냐, 인간아!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,으음...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,그러게요...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,반이 달라서
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,교실에서 어떤지는\N그다지 잘 모르지만요
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,누군가랑 같이 있는 모습을\N본 적이 없긴 하네요...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,괴롭힘당하고\N그런 일은 없거든요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,다행이다~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨가\N먼저 못 나서는 것도 있어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,다들, 다가가기\N어려워 하는 거 같다고 할지...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,어떻게 대하면 좋을지\N모르겠다는 느낌이라...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치, 재밌는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,그러니까요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 시작할게용~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,곡은 얘네 밴드~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,결속밴드의\N오리지널 곡이래요~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,짝짝짝~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 치자?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,기타 연습 같은 건\N같이 어울려주는데요
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만, 제 친구들이랑\N점심 먹자고 꼬셔보면
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,그때는\N또 안 된다면서...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,교실에 가봐도\N없고...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}-아아...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이 사람...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}즉흥으로 치는데도\N사운드에 전혀 망설임이 없어!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}엄청 자신감으로\N가득찬 연주...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내 연주를 확실하게\N떠받쳐주고 있구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}소리만 들어도 알겠어...\N즐기고 있다는 걸...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그에 비해, 나는...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}관객들한테\N비웃음 사지는 않을까...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}고개를 드는 것마저\N무서워...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,힘 내라...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐, 너\N무슨 소리 하는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,왠지, 기타 치는 애가\N불안해 보이길래 무심코...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"무심코"라니...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.32,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna천생연분\fs70\bord7\c&H5A656E&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(350,535)}암튼 팔림
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.32,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord7\c&H45675A&\3c&H87FFA1&\pos(845,650)}봇치쨩은 어떻게 됐어?{\fs25}\N\N{\fs60}오늘은 올 거야?{\fs25}\N\N{\fs60}신곡도 다 같이 맞춰보고 싶은데
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,후우...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮으려나...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그렇구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}처음부터\N적 같은 건 없었어...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내가 멋대로...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}히토리쨩, 눈이...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}단숨에 연주의 안정감이\N치솟았어
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}히토리쨩...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}원래는\N이렇게 치는구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}재밌는데...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}그거야...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}여기에 있는 건...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}네 연주를 듣고 싶어서\N멈춰서준 사람들이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}이 짧은 시간에 똑바로 알아채고\N결점을 극복하다니
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}굉장하잖아~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}이 아이는\N분명 뜰 거야...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}내 감은 잘 맞거든!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다들, 웃는 얼굴...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}앞으로도...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}잔뜩 라이브 하다 보면...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이런 표정들을\N잔뜩 볼 수 있게 되는 걸까...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,스페셜 라이브
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.99,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,300)\fs200\bord0\blur3\fscx500\fscy300\alpha&H60&\c&H394B59&\3c&H958999&\pos(1460,350)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.99,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\fad(10,300)\fn태 나무\fs70\bord6\c&H171C18&\3c&H958999&\pos(1460,400)}스페셜 라이브\N{\fs60}티켓 사줘!\N\N―――결속밴드―――\N\N{\fs50}1장 1500엔입니~다\N\N8/14 18시 시모키타자와 스태리
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}볼 수 있게 된다면...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}좋을 텐데...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩~\N좋더라~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,가..감사합니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다..다행이다...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}안 들켰어...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}한쪽 눈밖에\N안 뜨고 있던 거!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 왜 그럼~?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,아..아뇨, 아니에요...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}죄송합니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그렇게 금방 바로\N전부 바꾸는 건 무리예요!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,저기~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 옝!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,이 라이브 티켓\N사도 될까요?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,2장 주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,잉...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,잘 됐네, 히토리쨩~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,어라~?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,감동해서\N프리징 걸림~?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,1장에 1,500엔이니까\N3,000엔입니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,맞지?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,헉, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,저..쩌기요!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,정말 괜찮으세요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.4,979.12)}사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958.08,978.82)}사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.76,978.8)}사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958.04,980.8)}사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.26,981.66)}사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958.68,978.02)}사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958.16,980.9)}사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,사사사주셔도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,헤...\N히토리쨩, 집요하다~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그치만, 그게...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,길거리 공연은\N처음 봤는데요
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,엄청 좋았어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,이번에 한다는 라이브도\N열심히 하시길 기대할게요!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,열심히 할게요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,아까 그 곡도 하나요?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!\N합니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,기대하고 있을게요!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,저렇게 반짝거리는 시대가\N나한테도 있었을 텐데~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘밤은\N울분풀이 술 달린다아...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 왜 우세요...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,미안, 미안!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,금방 행복 스파이럴\N빨 테니까!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그거 분명\N몸에 안 좋을걸요...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,실례합니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서는\N라이브하지 말아주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}겨..경찰!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.61,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿죄송합니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,체포당해!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,안 당해, 안 당해~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐, 그래도\N혼났으니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,이쯤에서 끝낼까!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아, 맞다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}들떠서\N잊고 있었는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아직 앞으로\N1장 더 남아 있었지...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그..그래도\N4장이나 팔았잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}처음 해본 것 치고는\N잘한 거지~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,마지막 한 장은\N내가 살게!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,그걸로 목표 할당량\N달성하는 거지?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?\N괘..괜찮으세요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,물론이지~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,난 평소에 신쥬쿠를 거점으로\N활동하니까 가까운데다
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,이 라이브 하우스라면\N잘 알거든!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,어...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,가..감사합니다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,오니코로 5팩치를\N뛰어넘는 라이브~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,기대하고 있을게♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,또 같이 라이브하장~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,바이바이, 히토리쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}신기한 사람이었지...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}역시 밴드맨이란 건...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}멋지다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,어...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 사니까\N돈 다 떨어져버렸어~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,전철값만\N좀 빌려주라~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:57.98,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿라이브 보러 갔을 때\N갚을게여~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이 전개...\N어째 낯설지 않은데...
