Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,굉장하다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}오늘, 연습에 못 가서\N죄송합니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그리고
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}티켓\N전부 팔았습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}송신~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}라이브...\N성공하게 해주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1425,980)}「그리고」...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1425,980)}「티켓 전부 팔았습니다」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1425,980)}..라는데요?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1425,980)}봇치쨩...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1425,980)}이거 분명\N거짓말 하는 거겠지...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1425,980)}글지
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,역시...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,이 로인이 너무\N압박감을 줬던 걸지도...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,가엾게도...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,내일 연습 때는...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,다들 다정하게\N맞이해주자!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.14,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,980)\fad(00,600)}-네!\N-응...
